Provide file-based storage
NFS exports and SMB files shares.

# SAMBA

Install the samba package

```
yum install samba
```

Samba Daemons and Services

smbd
nmb
winbindd

```
systemctl enable smb nmb
```

Allow samba serice.

```
firewall-cmd --permanent --add-service=samba
firewall-cmd --reload
```
